show.description: In the shadows of a crumbling asylum, a mother’s final letters unravel a tale of stolen identity, betrayal, and lost love. As Varun uncovers the devastating truth, he learns his real daughter was replaced—and his past, manipulated. But just when the lies seem unstoppable, a familiar face returns… and Tushita’s twin is ready to expose everything.
